OL,3,CIrish premier Micheal Martin to meet
OL,4,CUkraine's Volodymyr Zelensky in Kyiv
OL,6,FIrish premier Micheal Martin is to
OL,7,Fmeet Ukrainian President Volodymyr
OL,8,FZelensky in Kyiv on Thursday as
OL,9,Fpressure mounts on Ireland over
OL,10,Falumina exports.
OL,12,FThe two leaders are expected to
OL,13,Fdiscuss Russia's war against Ukraine
OL,14,Fand how Ireland's presidency of the
OL,15,FCouncil of the EU can support
OL,16,FUkraine's sovereignty.
OL,26,@kD@TrpnD@Trp
