FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784767669
OL,3,CIrish premier Micheal Martin to meet
OL,4,CUkraine's Volodymyr Zelensky in Kyiv
OL,6,FMr Martin will also meet Ukraine's new
OL,7,Fprime minister Serhii Koretskyi,
OL,8,Fformer head of state energy company
OL,9,FNaftogaz, who was appointed last week
OL,10,Fduring a controversial government
OL,11,Freshuffle.
OL,13,FMr Zelensky has cited Mr Koretskyi's
OL,14,Frecord in the energy sector and said
OL,15,Fhe was best prepared to guide Ukraine
OL,16,Fthrough another winter, when Russian
OL,17,Fattacks on the power grid intensify.
OL,26,@kD@Trp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784767669
OL,3,CIrish premier Micheal Martin to meet
OL,4,CUkraine's Volodymyr Zelensky in Kyiv
OL,6,FThe Irish leader will also visit the
OL,7,FUkrainian parliament, the Verkhovna
OL,8,FRada, and meet its speaker, Ruslan
OL,9,FStefanchuk, where they are expected to
OL,10,Fdiscuss EU accession negotiations.
OL,12,FThe Taoiseach will also visit civilian
OL,13,Fareas in Kyiv damaged in recent
OL,14,Fattacks by Russia and meet members of
OL,15,Fthe Irish community in Kyiv.
OL,26,@kD@Trp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784767669
OL,3,CIrish premier Micheal Martin to meet
OL,4,CUkraine's Volodymyr Zelensky in Kyiv
OL,6,FThe visit comes as pressure increases
OL,7,Fon Ireland over the Russian-owned
OL,8,Frefinery in Limerick, Aughinish
OL,9,FAlumina, over allegations that alumina
OL,10,Ffrom the plant is being used to supply
OL,11,Fthe manufacturers of missiles, tanks
OL,12,Fand aircraft being used against
OL,13,FUkraine.
OL,15,FDuring Mr Zelensky's visit to Dublin
OL,16,Fearlier this month, he said he was
OL,17,Fhopeful for "a positive result for us"
OL,18,Fin the investigation carried out by
OL,19,FIreland into alumina exports.
OL,26,@kD@TrpyD@MOUyD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784767669
OL,3,CIrish premier Micheal Martin to meet
OL,4,CUkraine's Volodymyr Zelensky in Kyiv
OL,6,FSpeaking ahead of his visit, Mr Martin
OL,7,Fsaid Ukraine was a "central priority"
OL,8,Ffor Ireland's presidency of the EU as
OL,9,Fhe praised Ukraine's courage in
OL,10,Fresisting "relentless" Russian attacks.
OL,12,FHe condemned the Russian attacks that
OL,13,Fhad "intensified" on Kyiv and
OL,14,Felsewhere in recent weeks.
OL,16,F"My visit to Kyiv early in the term of
OL,17,FIreland's presidency of the EU is
OL,18,Fimportant to underline the EU's and
OL,19,FIreland's continuing solidarity with
OL,20,Fthe Ukrainian government and the
OL,21,Fpeople of Ukraine," the Taoiseach said.
OL,26,@kD@TrpoD@TOUoD@eO]rD@KOUrD@VO]uD@EOUuD@
OL,26,AQO]xD@AOU}D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784767669
OL,3,CIrish premier Micheal Martin to meet
OL,4,CUkraine's Volodymyr Zelensky in Kyiv
OL,6,F"Support for Ukraine is a central
OL,7,Fpriority of the Irish presidency of
OL,8,Fthe EU."
OL,10,FMr Martin also said that there would
OL,11,Fbe increased pressure on Russia to end
OL,12,Fits war through "further robust and
OL,13,Ftargeted sanctions".
OL,15,F"This visit is an opportunity to hear
OL,16,Fdirectly from President Zelensky and
OL,17,FPrime Minister Koretskyi about the
OL,18,Fsituation on the ground and the needs
OL,19,Fof the Ukrainian government as it
OL,20,Ffaces into a fifth year of defending
OL,21,Fits country against Russian aggression.
OL,26,@kD@TrpnD@AOUpD@HO]tD@QOUuD@SO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784767669
OL,3,CIrish premier Micheal Martin to meet
OL,4,CUkraine's Volodymyr Zelensky in Kyiv
OL,6,F"I will reiterate to President
OL,7,FZelensky that during our EU
OL,8,Fpresidency, Ireland is strongly
OL,9,Fcommitted to advancing Ukraine's path
OL,10,Fto EU accession and to building
OL,11,Fconsensus to ensure that Ukraine has
OL,12,Fthe support it needs.
OL,14,F"We will also work on increasing
OL,15,Fpressure on Russia to end its war of
OL,16,Faggression, including through further
OL,17,Frobust and targeted sanctions.
OL,26,@kD@TrpnD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784767669
OL,3,CIrish premier Micheal Martin to meet
OL,4,CUkraine's Volodymyr Zelensky in Kyiv
OL,6,F"I also look forward to discussing
OL,7,Fwith President Zelensky how Ireland,
OL,8,Fincluding through our EU presidency
OL,9,Fand our participation in the Coalition
OL,10,Fof Willing, can support efforts to
OL,11,Fachieve the shared goal of a just and
OL,12,Flasting peace for the people of
OL,13,FUkraine which respects Ukraine's
OL,14,Fsovereignty and territorial integrity.
OL,16,F"I have always been clear that we
OL,17,Fcannot tolerate borders being changed
OL,18,Fby force and that we will stand with
OL,19,FUkraine for as long as it takes.
OL,26,@kD@TrpnD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784767669
OL,3,CIrish premier Micheal Martin to meet
OL,4,CUkraine's Volodymyr Zelensky in Kyiv
OL,6,F"I will also review with President
OL,7,FZelensky progress on the
OL,8,Fimplementation of the 2030 Roadmap on
OL,9,FIreland-Ukraine Partnership, which we
OL,10,Fsigned during the president's
OL,11,Fhistorical visit to Ireland last
OL,12,FDecember, and what further support
OL,13,FIreland can provide to Ukraine
OL,14,Fbuilding on the over 500 million euro
OL,15,Fin bilateral funding provided to date
OL,16,Ffor humanitarian needs, non-lethal
OL,17,Fmilitary assistance and to support
OL,18,FUkraine's critical energy
OL,19,Finfrastructure."
OL,26,@kD@TrpnD@AOU{D@PO]
